            "success": "The creature is frightened 1.",
            "text": "The marauder unleashes a terrifying battle cry. Each enemy in a 30-foot emanation must attempt a DC 21 Will save. Regardless of the results, creatures are temporarily immune for 1 minute.",
            "traits": [
